  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the functional characteristics and utility of upper and lower limb prosthetic
      devices (advanced bionic and current clinical standard-of-care) that incorporate
      physiologically relevant touch and/or movement feedback.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
